ious midweek meal, or for adding to a weekend barbecue when extra guests arrive! For other great burger recipes refer to Cookidoo.","If mixture is wet and difficult to handle, use floured hands to shape the patties."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","1h 10m","8 portions"]}